 Danni Menzies, 33, has taken to Instagram to show off her toned legs in a series of photos taken in front of glamorous sports cars. She was also seen standing side by side with former Top Gear Stig, Ben Collins. The A Place In The Sun star was pictured in a mini black and white polka dot skirt as she smiled for the camera. She teamed the look with a collared leather jacket and black top alongside long black boots which highlighted the stars’ well-defined legs. The presenter accessorised with a small necklace as she wore her signature blonde tresses Danni had the snaps taken as she visited the Goodwood Festival of Speed today.  